            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Similarly, we don’t do this work to entertain, amuse, or distract audiences, nor do we do it to comfort, placate, and reassure partisan audiences who never want to face inconvenient truths.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "We do this work to inform, motivate, and empower our readers to force changes that improve the world.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "That’s what’s happening right now, thanks to our paying subscribers’ support and activism. So let’s keep the pressure on.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
